abstract: Eat deliciously on Christmas — and on the days leading up to it, with sesame-glazed duck legs, baked mushrooms and beans, and a breakfast feed from Melissa Clark.
snippet: Eat deliciously on Christmas — and on the days leading up to it, with sesame-glazed duck legs, baked mushrooms and beans, and a breakfast feed from Melissa Clark.
lead_paragraph: Good morning. It’s been a difficult month for my crowd, and it looked for a time as if we’d lose Christmas entirely. But the tree’s now trimmed with favorite ornaments (A ski-jumping bear from Quebec! A ceramic dolphin from Florida!), and the whole place smells of forest and cinnamon. There’s lots of jing-jing-jingling. The dog’s asleep in front of the fire.

abstract: The party was part of a memorial for a man who was killed in April, the authorities said.
snippet: The party was part of a memorial for a man who was killed in April, the authorities said.
lead_paragraph: A house party on the South Side of Chicago was meant to remember a man who was fatally shot during a carjacking in April, the authorities said. But the memorial itself erupted into violence early Sunday after at least two gunmen opened fire, wounding 13 people, four of them critically.

abstract: Japanese hotel chain Unizo Holdings said on Sunday it had received a friendly buyout offer from U.S. investment fund Lone Star, a deal that could end a five-month takeover battle involving Blackstone Group, Fortress Investment Group and activist investor Elliott Management.
snippet: Japanese hotel chain Unizo Holdings said on Sunday it had received a friendly buyout offer from U.S. investment fund Lone Star, a deal that could end a five-month takeover battle involving Blackstone Group, Fortress Investment Group and activist i...
lead_paragraph: TOKYO — Japanese hotel chain Unizo Holdings said on Sunday it had received a friendly buyout offer from U.S. investment fund Lone Star, a deal that could end a five-month takeover battle involving Blackstone Group, Fortress Investment Group and activist investor Elliott Management.
headline_main: Lone Star Emerges as White-Knight Bidder for Japanese Hotel Chain Unizo
